Package listeners

Interface ReachabilityStateChangeListener

public interface ReachabilityStateChangeListener
The listener interface for receiving reachabilityStateChange events. The class that is interested in processing a reachabilityStateChange event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addReachabilityStateChangeListener method. When the reachabilityStateChange event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
